What, did they fart in your general direction? I mean, come on, in EQ *taunting* is just part of the RP. If you can't beat them, then duel them, and yes, you'll lose if you are too low, but at least you fought honorably. Btw, in *reality* the minute you hit your own guard, you'd be damned forever as an outcast or killed, so the &quot;RP&quot; way to solve it is not training.<br>
<br>
If there's more to the story than them just calling you names, then post it. But if all they did was taunt you and call you names, then now's the time for you to learn that causing experience loss is *never* appropriate. If you want to train folks, go to Sullon Zek.<br>
