<br>
But training guards on them... as Isharra said, you had to strike a guard to get it to follow you.  Did you stay to take the faction hit when they were killed or did you zone out after training to avoid the results of your actions?  Intentional training is NEVER right whether they were able to take care of the train or not.  <br>
